deck: Re-established from First Comics in the early 2010s and resumed publishing comics in 2015. Merged with Devil's Due to form Devil's Due/1First Comics, LLC.
description:
1First Comics was formed by Ken Levin in the early 2010s, resuming publishing from First Comics (1983-1992). In 2015, it was announced that 1First Comics would merge with Devil's Due Entertainment to form "Devil's Due/1First Comics, LLC."

There are now three co-existing websites:

  • www.1firstcomics.com
  • www.devilsdue-1first.com
  • www.devilsdue.net

All websites already use the new combined logo however, some titles are still published by the individual companies and other titles, such as Public Relations, are already published by the new merger.
name: 1First Comics
